OL,3,CSeven boys charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed outside mosque
OL,6,FPolice have charged seven teenagers
OL,7,Fwith murder so far, after an 18-year-
OL,8,Fold boy was stabbed outside a mosque.
OL,10,FZeshan Afzal was stabbed in Smethwick,
OL,11,Foutside Jamia Masjid, on Oldbury Road
OL,12,Fshortly before 9pm on 20 February.
OL,14,FTwo other men, aged 19 and 22, were
OL,15,Ftaken to hospital following the
OL,16,Fincident with injuries not thought to
OL,17,Fbe life-threatening.
OL,19,FPolice charged a 17-year-old boy with
OL,20,Fmurder on Tuesday - meaning seven in
OL,21,Ftotal have been charged.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
