OL,3,CSeven boys charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed outside mosque
OL,6,FIn addition, three boys were arrested
OL,7,Fon Wednesday morning - one aged 13 and
OL,8,Ftwo aged 17, on suspicion of murder.
OL,10,FWest Midlands Police said it is
OL,11,Fcontinuing to appeal for information,
OL,12,Fwith members of the public urged to
OL,13,Fsubmit mobile phone or dash cam
OL,14,Ffootage.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the force added:
OL,17,F"You can also contact us on 101
OL,18,Fquoting log number 4896 of 20
OL,19,FFebruary."
